  "about_item": [
    "2-IN-1 CARRIER & CAR SEAT: Not only a stylish bag – seat-belt loops are naturally integrated into the delicate design so you can secure the carrier in the car for safer travel.",
    "FOR CATS & SMALL DOGS: Sized for pets up to 16 lb, giving kittens, cats, toy breeds, and small puppies a secure, cozy ride.",
    "STYLISH & MODERN LOOK: Refined detailing – smart enough for airport terminals and everyday errands.",
    "AIRLINE CABIN SIZE & LUGGAGE SLEEVE: Soft-sided design with ventilated panels fits under many airline seats (17\" × 9\" × 11\"); always confirm your carrier’s rules before flying. A luggage sleeve slides over your suitcase handle to ease your load and keep the carrier steady while you roll through the airport.",
    "HIGH-QUALITY MATERIALS & HARDWARE: High-quality faux leather dual handles and accents for grip and durability; a handle connector/wrap to join the handles for comfort; an adjustable, removable shoulder strap in tough webbing with reinforced hardware; and YKK self-locking zippers for smooth operation that won’t creep open – plus a fluorescent safety leash to keep pets secure.",
    "VENTILATION & PRIVACY CONTROL: Breathable mesh on multiple sides promotes airflow and visibility. When you need shade or fewer distractions, roll-up flaps can cover the mesh – great for calming nervous pets in busy terminals, blocking bright light for naps, or limiting drafts.",
    "COMFORTABLE, YEAR-ROUND MAT: Reversible insert with a cooling summer side made from rattan-style woven bamboo fiber (plant-based and eco-friendly) and a cozy winter side – plus a sturdy base that reduces sagging.",
    "BUILT-IN POOP-BAG DISPENSER: Dedicated pocket with a feed-through slot keeps waste bags handy for quick, tidy cleanups on walks and trips."
  ],
