        "position": 5,
        "title": "Super Happy",
        "text": "This really looks high end. It’s quite expensive but it’s very functional and beautifully made. It’s very solid and collapses flat. I am very happy with my purchase.",
        "rating": 5,
        "date": "March 7, 2026",
        "author": "Wenhamhome",
        "author_link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AESYEC7K2BRNSKWAYS6WN6NUNGKQ",
        "author_image": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default.png",
